Title: Energy Levels and Wave Functions of Vector Bosons in Homogeneous

Magnetic FieldAuthors: K.Sogut, A.Havare, I.Acikgoz

Comments: 13 pages, no figures

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 43 (2002) 3952-3962

We aimed to obtain the energy levels of spin-1 particles moving in a constantmagnetic field. The method used here is completely algebraic. In the process toobtain the energy levels the wave function is choosen in terms of LaguerrePolynomials.